ly:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">5.</span></span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(22, 121, 255);font-weight: bold;\">报名方式</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-size: 15px;line-height: 26px;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);margin: 0px 0px 4px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">📮</span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">点击文末“阅读原文”或扫描下方二维码填写问卷</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.982532751091703\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"458\" style=\"width: 195px;height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"458\" data-height=\"450\" data-backw=\"458\" data-backh=\"450\" data-imgfileid=\"100009899\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aa7f3e4e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlRIrvTGkm9vectibo8Yleiasaxp4z63N1LoC2rAOJESlPyQJVjkh2lleoegc8ic5g2Ep3XdFhBTrjgX3EtnJicVH50lSdjmicG5zXcIwUEdibmFnk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(50, 120, 71);font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 8px;font-size: 22px;padding-bottom: 12px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么是现在？</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">Physical AI 正从论文走向现实。小龙虾让开发者可以用开源工具栈快速构建机器人应用，Pony-Alpha-2 为具身场景带来了更强的工具调用与长程规划能力，智能硬件生态日渐丰富。大模型驱动物理世界的基础设施，正在逐渐拼齐。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">下一步，我们需要更多真实世界的检验，让 AI 面对延迟、噪声、碰撞和误解。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">其实，这个比赛正是源于我们的日常生活。最近，智谱的一位实习生用Pony-Alpha-2+小龙虾+机器人，为全公司解决了一个订餐的小麻烦，他把过程记录了下来。</span></p>\n  <p></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们看着它想：如果小龙虾一下午就能学会点餐和跑腿，那么给它一整天和一整个房间呢？</span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">首届比赛大概率会很“惨烈”。机器人可能会走错路、听不懂话、把啤酒洒一地，这就是意义所在。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:26px;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">第一步可能都很笨拙，但所有伟大的东西，都是从这里开始的。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智谱发起'A Room for Claw'创新赛事，邀请全球开发者使用搭载 Pony-Alpha-2 大模型的机器人，在真实啤酒屋场景中完成服务任务，探索具身智能的物理世界应用。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智谱发起'A Room for Claw'创新赛事，邀请全球开发者使用搭载 Pony-Alpha-2 大模型的机器人，在真实啤酒屋场景中完成服务任务，探索具身智能的物理世界应用。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了智谱 z.ai 发起的'A Room for Claw'创新社会实验赛事。该赛事邀请开发者操控搭载 Pony-Alpha-2 大模型和 OpenClaw 框架的机器人，在真实啤酒屋环境中完成听懂指令、提供服务和主动感知等任务。比赛设有两项 Bench：Beer Bench（取啤酒送到位）和 Tips Bench（让顾客开心给小费），并设有 3 万元、2 万元、1 万元的奖金。文章还阐述了举办该赛事的背景——Physical AI 正从论文走向现实，需要更多真实世界的检验，以及比赛的灵感来源（一位实习生用机器人为公司解决订餐问题的案例）。",
